        "action": "Allow single parents to change a child's name without the other parent's consent",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "To allow single parents to change their child\u2019s surname without the other parent's permission, without having to go through the court procedure, even if the other parent is listed on the birth certificate. This is particularly important especially where domestic violence and abuse has occurred.",
